{"tid":563611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拜年時親戚們的失禮事","createTime":"2018-02-17T06:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T08:10:16.000Z","uid":86545,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"57574731595539042a59e057601787f98d3aa7a5","tid":563611,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"每年拜年, 一大班親戚朋友都會講一講自己仔女的學業之類。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  親戚們, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  姑姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  表妹<br />\n<br />\n今年個姑姐係度講自己會女入左港大 marking <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (親戚a):咁叻女 !入港大, 中文即係咩科<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呀女快d講比大家聽你讀咩啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知中文係咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點會唔知架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁真係無中文, hku space marking and business 囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係叻啦入港大<br />\n<br />\n而我地一班表兄弟妹就明白到真相...表妹只係一個太空人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a94afbf956991e755ebca82c2375f7143802df","tid":563611,"uid":106482,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"Marking?"},{"pid":"ad0e02c550d63f702357e2f15c54364bef1921da","tid":563611,"uid":56240,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"hku <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">space</span> 超勁"},{"pid":"fd80f0344ba251120628d9bd7363925b351b4b52","tid":563611,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a94afbf956991e755ebca82c2375f7143802df","tid":563611,"uid":106482,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2